Wee haue therefore caused all the goods and Marchandizes chargeable with the said poundage either broght in, or transported out of this Kingdome, together with the seuerall kinds, qualities, numbers, weights, measures and contents of the same, and the values, prices, and Rates thereof to be particularly entred and expressed in this present Booke, containing in leaues on both sides 
         ••
      to the entent his Maiestie may henceforth bee iustly aunswered of the said poundage, according to the tenor of the said Act of Parliament;
